    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278532</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>くっ……！
一体、ヤツはどこへ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guh... Where did that freak go...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ご報告します！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Reporting, sir!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;及び&lt;Red&gt;トーティス&lt;White&gt;、
その他、多くの街が
魔物に襲撃されています！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hords of monsters have been reported
attacking &lt;Red&gt;Euclid&lt;White&gt; and &lt;Red&gt;Totus&lt;White&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうやら、その魔物たちは
&lt;Red&gt;スルト深林&lt;White&gt;から来ていると
思われます！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We believe these monsters are coming
from the &lt;Red&gt;Deep Forest Surt&lt;White&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278940</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;スルト深林&lt;White&gt;だと？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The &lt;Red&gt;Deep Forest Surt&lt;White&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278940</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>確かあの森には、
無害な獣しか住んで
いなかったはずでは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Only harmless creatures live there...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まさか、魔界の扉……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It can't be... He's after the
Otherworldly Gate...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの森の深くに
魔界と人間界をつなぐ
扉があると言います！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The door that connects the
human and demon realm
lies within that forest!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>封印が解かれた……
魔界の民を操る……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He wants to break the seal on the door...
"To control a legion of monsters"...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ブレイナーが
言っていたのは
このことなのか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Is this what Brainer is after!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>このままでは、
&lt;Red&gt;トーティス&lt;White&gt;や&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;で
多くの犠牲者が出ます！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If this keeps up, there will be innumerable
casualties for both Euclid and Totus!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279488</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>全軍を各方面に回せ！
魔物の排除と、
住民の保護を最優先だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Assemble all units! We will attack
the monsters and defend the
citizens at any cost!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さん……わたしたちは
&lt;Red&gt;スルト深林&lt;White&gt;へ行った方が
いいのではないでしょうか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Cless&gt;...Don't you think we should
head to the &lt;Red&gt;Deep Forest Surt&lt;White&gt;? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうか……ブレイナーを
捕まえないと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right...If we can't capture Brainer,
then this will be really bad...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ええ、それに扉を閉じなければ、
多くの魔物たちがこちらの
世界へ流れ出てきます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes...if we don't close the door, the
world will be swarmed with monsters.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280036</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、村は彼らに任せて、
僕たちは魔物を
抑えに行った方がいいね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's leave the protecting the cities to them.
We'll handle the source of the monsters.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい。それでは
&lt;Red&gt;12星座の塔&lt;White&gt;へ行きましょう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right! Then we should get going
to the &lt;Red&gt;Tower of the Zodiac&lt;White&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>12星座の……
ルナのところに……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Red&gt;Tower of the Zodiac&lt;White&gt;...
Isn't that where Luna is?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280344</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔界の扉はルナの光で
封印されていたはずです。
彼女の力を借りなければ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Luna's light can help us seal the
Otherworldly Gate. We need to ask
her to lend us her powers again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕たちは、これから
&lt;Red&gt;12星座の塔&lt;White&gt;へ行く。
君たちとはここでお別れだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We'll be leaving for the &lt;Red&gt;Tower of the
Zodiac&lt;White&gt;. I bid you farewell, everyone.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>急ごう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's hurry.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたし、行くよ、
いいでしょ？　エト</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Can I go with them, Eto?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きみたちは
虹輪を消さなきゃ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, you need to stop the Prism Ring!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、今、この世界は
大変なことになってるんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I know, but we can't just leave
this world in trouble, can we?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それを目の前で
放っておくなんて、わたし……
できないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't have people suffering in front of
me like this... I WON'T abandon them!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>280960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>行こうぜ……！
&lt;Cless&gt;さんたちの後を追おう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go...! Let's follow Mister
&lt;Cless&gt; and Miss &lt;Mint&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……&lt;Dio&gt;、
もう平気なの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, are you sure
you're alright?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ……
確かめなきゃ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes...I just need to make sure...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_049&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしたの、&lt;Dio&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What do you need to make sure of?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281284</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_050&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんでもない……
&lt;Red&gt;12星座の塔&lt;White&gt;に行こう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nothin' of course! Let's go to the
&lt;Red&gt;Tower of the Zodiac&lt;White&gt; already!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_051&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルルー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281416</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_050_052&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……確かめなきゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I need to make sure...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
